On KB [Customize Exports to PDF|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/ConfCloud/Customize+Exports+to+PDF], under the *Disabling Table of Contents* section, an incorrect rule is described.

 

*How it is:*
{code:java}
div.toc-macro
{
display: none;
}{code}
*How it should be:*
{code:java}
div.toc
{
display: none;
}{code}
 

Please refer to issue below for more information:
 *   [I want to export to PDF. I don't want a TOC|https://getsupport.atlassian.com/browse/JST-282595]
